To build simply call make in root directory.

This Project requires: 
	clang++-12 libsdl2-dev ninja-build

Controls:
	WASD: Move the Camera 
	Space: Raise the Camera
	CTRL: Lower the Camera

	Mouse Movement: Rotate the Camera
	Q: Toggle Capture the mouse for ease of control

	1: Toggle Post Processing Mode
		- By defult edge detection
		- swap to no processing
	2: Swap Ortho view


	ESC: Exit the program


Code Reuse:
	To load textures I use stb_image.h from Sean Barrett: https://github.com/nothings
